title: American Horror Story: #WitchBitchTrilogy Vol.1
author: Wil Heuser
comment: Wow, I'm impressed! You did an amazing impersonation of her character here. Loved it!
I absolutely love your Jessica Lange impersonation. It's like you were born to play her. Can't wait to see more!
PLEASE could you continue the the trilogy? It's really good and I need the other two videos.
description: Part one of AHS:Coven Parody. The very best of Jessica Lang.. follow on twitter @wilheuser
